            <div class="post-content-inner">
              
              <div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">Yeah, don't invent this stuff yourself, date and time is horrible, and the more your know, the more you go EWWWyuckyBLARGH.</div><br />There's also the bonus that when you get hit with a leap year bug, you can point to the vendor (and all the other companies that are much &quot;better&quot; than you and still got hit) instead of taking it on the chin like any unlucky asshole who had that issue in homecrafted date-time software last year. Don't underestimate the ability to CYA on these things.

              

              
              
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
